squad.Discovery.implications | hasValue | A literal /tmp/cold-judge clone forces every wikilink, path, and breadcrumb to be evaluated by what's actually pushed to origin — not what's locally in the working tree. The clone IS the threshold. Cross-test pattern works for any soul-corpus.
